"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Ointment, topical, as acetate [strength expressed as base]: 1% (30 g)",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justify;\">",
